CHANGES
	Important changes since last release

doc/load.doc
	Information on dynamicly loading code into SNOBOL4
	(also installed in /usr/local/lib/snobol4/)

doc/snobol4.1
	man page for snobol4.
	describes changes from the SNOBOL4 reference ("green book").

doc/snobol4.0
	text formatted output of snobol4 man page

doc/snobol4.html
	WWW HyperText formatted output of snobol4.1

doc/snobol4.ps
	PostScript formatted output of snobol4.1

doc/ports.doc
	status of ports to various systems.

doc/porting.doc
	information on porting to a new system,
	particularly the usage of Makefile variables and m4 macros.

doc/porting.ps
	porting information in PostScript.

doc/porting.html
	porting information in HTML.

